      • difference

        public IntHashSet difference(IntHashSet collection)
        Fast Path set difference for comparison with another IntHashSet.

        NB: garbage free in the identical case, allocates otherwise.

        Parameters:
        collection - the other set to subtract
        Returns:
        null if identical, otherwise the set of differences
